  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Senju Clan, level 4+</p><p>The blood of the Second Hokage, runs through your veins, providing you unmatched Wisdom. <br />You cannot take this feat if you have another Legacy Senju clan feat. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• When you would deal Earth damage with your Wood Release clan feature, you can choose to instead deal Cold Damage.</p><p>• Select a number of Ninjutsu with the Water release keyword that you know, equal to your Proficiency Bonus, that does not have the Hijutsu keyword. Those Jutsu gains the Hijutsu keyword and counts as a Senju Hijutsu for the purpose of triggering Senju Clan Features. You can switch these jutsu when you complete a long rest.</p>",
